<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>隔离级别</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在典型的应用程序中，多个事务并发运行，经常会操作相同的数据来完成各自的任务。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"></span></span><br></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">并发虽然是必须的，但可能会导致以下的问题：</span></span></li>
</ul>

                                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">T1</span><span

<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><strong>注</strong></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>不可重复读与幻读的区别</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">不可重复读的重点是发生事务修改，同样的条件</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">你读取过的数据</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">再次读取出来发现值不一样了</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">幻读的重点在于发生新增或者删除事务，同样的条件</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">第</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">1</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">次和第</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">2</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">次读出来的记录数不一样</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">从总的结果来看</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">似乎不可重复读和幻读都表现为两次读取的结果不一致。但如果你从控制的角度来看</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">两者的区别就比较大。&nbsp;</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:square">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对于前者</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">只需要锁住满足条件的记录。&nbsp;</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对于后者</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">要锁住满足条件及其相近的记录</span></span></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>只读</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">如果事务只对后端的数据库进行该操作，数据库可以利用事务的只读特性来进行一些特定的优化。通过将事务设置为只读，你就可以给数据库一个机会，让它应用它认为合适的优化措施</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>事务超时</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">为了使应用程序很好地运行，事务不能运行太长的时间，默认超时时间为</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">-1</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">因为事务可能涉及对后端数据库的锁定，所以长时间的事务会不必要的占用数据库资源。</span></span>
    </li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">事务超时就是事务的一个定时器，表示一个业务方法最长的执行时间，在特定时间内事务如果没有执行完毕，那么就会自动回滚事务，而不是一直等待其结束</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:black">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:black"><strong>回滚规则</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">规则定义了哪些异常会导致事务回滚而哪些不会。默认情况下，事务只有遇到运行期异常时才会回滚，而在遇到检查型异常时不会回滚</span></span>
    </li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">但是你可以声明事务在遇到特定的检查型异常时像遇到运行期异常那样回滚。同样，你还可以声明事务遇到特定的异常不回滚，即使这些异常是运行期异常</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">异常分类：</span></span>
        <ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
            <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Error</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">： 严重错误。
                        回滚事务。</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Exception :
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">异常类，可以出来的异常情况</span></span>
                <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
                    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">运行时异常</span></span></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:144px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#24292e"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">RuntimeException</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和他的子类都是运行时异常， 在程序执行过程中抛出的异常。 常见的运行时异常：</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> NullPoinerException , NumberFormatException ,
                ArithmeticException, IndexOutOfBoundsException.</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 80px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">受查异常</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 160px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#24292e"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">编写</span><span

                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">IOException , SQLException ,
                FileNotFoundException</span></span></span></p>

<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">方法中抛出了运行时异常，
                事务回滚，其他情况（正常执行方法，受查异常）就是提交事务。</span></span></li>
